'''Cinema Paradiso''' is a UK-based [[DVD-by-mail]] company which specialises in world and arthouse cinema but also caters for mainstream tastes as well with over 80,000 titles films and 5000+ [[Blu-ray]] high definition titles available. They operate a system which divides film info for each title by genre and special features on the disc. They also carry a list of over 5000 foreign language DVDs from Hollywood to Bollywood, Argentina to Vietnam, Tajikistan to Mongolia.<ref>{{cite web|title=What's on TV? Let's look in the mailbox|url=https://www.theguardian.com/business/2008/jan/13/amazon|publisher=theguardian.com|accessdate=13 May 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Review|url=http://www.choose.net/media/guide/features/lovefilm-review.html|publisher=Choose.net}}</ref>
==History== Cinema Paradiso is privately owned company which was established in 2003 in [[Lewisham|Lewisham, South London]] and is currently headquartered in [[Brentford]], UK. In 2005 the company bought Zoovies.net,<ref>{{cite web|title=Movie fans invited to celebrate CinemaParadiso.co.uk 10-year anniversary|url=http://www.prweb.com/releases/2014/2/prweb11560844.htm|accessdate=13 May 2015}}</ref> and in the following year acquired DVDsToMe.
