'''''Studio 2M''''' (in [[Arabic language|Arabic]] 2M استوديو) is a [[Morocco|Moroccan]] song competition on [[2M TV]] television station for 10 consecutive years. It is equivalent to the French [[Star Academy]]. The first season started on 26 June 2004 and was presented that year by Imad Ntifi
